2.  add 1 twilight when you assign a minion to a skirmish<br />
3.  Place your hand beneath your draw deck & draw 4 cards.<br />
4.  +1 twilight for each mounted companion<br />
5.  Deep of Helm<br />
6.  Play a possession to draw a card<br />
7.  +2 Archery for each unbound companion over 3<br />
8.  Wizard&#39;s Vale<br />
9.  +2 twilight for each companion over 4<br />
<br />
